Gg_maniacal is a map with 3 main "corridors" or lines of fire. 2 side ones and a central "shooting range". There are lots of nooks to take cover in or camp in. 

The sides of the map also have a 2nd story. Snipers and "flankers" will learn to use this to their advantage.

Make a rush to the central bridge, and you'll find the one-way windows very helpful. You can see out but they cant see in!

Dont forget that the Terrorist and CounterTerrorist spawn-bunkers have oneway windows too. Especially when you have chosen the central lane.

Grua is spanish for crane.

This is a Gungame 4hm level. I made it small for close contact fighting (a quick game is a good game). I added a few camping and sniper spots for fair gameplay.

Caution, you cannot go for a swim in my version of Sydney harbour, the water is deadly ;). 

There is access onto the Tub Boats for all u campers but u can't hide on it. Be carefull not to fall into the water when you try to board them.

I made some custom textures of the Sydney skyline and added harbour soundscape for atmosphere.

Enjoy

Gg_lost_temple

This is a medium sized map that is open in the middle.  There are four “temple” structures that line the outside of the map and all face inward.  Each team spawns on opposite sides of the map, and everything is symmetrical.  Buy Zones have been included just so people can play the map FY style if they wish.

-	44 Spawns, 22 per a team
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview radar map
-	Cube Maps
-	3d Skybox
-       Buy Zones
-	Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat

You can find the AWP version of this map here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/112281
